sourcesContent: import { Component, OnInit } from '@angular/core'; import { RouterModule } from '@angular/router'; import { TokenServicesService } from 'src/app/_services/token-services.service'; @Component({ selector: 'app-mostrar-servicios', templateUrl: './mostrar-servicios.component.html', styleUrls: ['./mostrar-servicios.component.css'], }) export class MostrarServiciosComponent implements OnInit{ servicios?:string; constructor(private dataServices: TokenServicesService) {} getAllServices(){ this.dataServices.getServices().subscribe( positiveResult =>{ this.servicios = positiveResult; }, err => { this.servicios = JSON.parse(err.error).message; } ) } ngOnInit(): void { this.getAllServices(); } }
